ent supplied by the computed shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNComputedShapeSource"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesource","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNShape","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is an abstract class that represents a shape or annotation. Shapes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"constitute the content of a map — not only the overlays atop the map, but also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the content that forms the base map."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShape"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Data source for "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". This protocol defines two optional methods for fetching"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"data, one based on tile coordinates, and one based on a bounding box. Classes that implement this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"protocol must implement one, and only one of the methods. Methods on this protocol will not be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"called on main thread, they will be called on the caller’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"requestQueue"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"fragme